Sentiment-Based Trading Strategy with FinBERT and Alpaca

This project implements a sentiment-based trading strategy using FinBERT for sentiment analysis and Alpaca for trading execution. The strategy is backtested using Yahoo Finance data.

Requirements
Python 3.6 or higher
Lumibot
Alpaca
dotenv
FinBERT

Other dependencies specified in the code
Installation
Clone the repository and navigate to the project directory.

Create a virtual environment and activate it:
python3 -m venv env
source env/bin/activate  # On Windows, use `env\Scripts\activate`

Install the required packages:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Set up your environment variables:
Create a .env file in the project directory with the following content:
BASE_URL=<your_alpaca_base_url>
API_KEY=<your_alpaca_api_key>
API_SECRET=<your_alpaca_api_secret>